export default {
    algorithms: [{
        _id: '1',
        name: "Sequential Search",
        algo: "def sequentialSearch(array, searchingNumber):" +
            "found = False" +
            "   i = 0\n" +
                    "   index = -1\n" +
            "    while i < len(array) and not found:\n" +
            "        if array[i] == searchingNumber:\n" +
            "            index = i\n" +
            "            found = True\n" +
            "\n" +
            "        i += 1\n" +
            "\n" +
            "    if index != int(-1):\n" +
            "        print(\"Found at position: \" + str(index))\n" +
            "\n" +
            "    else:\n" +
            "        print(\"Not found!\")\n" +
            "\n"
        },
        {
            _id: '2',
            name: "Binary Search",
            algo: "def binarySearch(array, searchingNumber):\n" +
                "    found = False\n" +
                "    index = -1\n" +
                "    left = 0\n" +
                "    right = len(array) - 1\n" +
                "\n" +
                "    while left <= right and not found:\n" +
                "        mid = (left + right) // 2\n" +
                "\n" +
                "        if array[mid] < searchingNumber:\n" +
                "            left = mid + 1\n" +
                "\n" +
                "        elif array[mid] > searchingNumber:\n" +
                "            right = mid - 1\n" +
                "\n" +
                "        else:\n" +
                "            print(\"Found at: \" + str(mid))\n" +
                "            found = True\n"
        },
        {
            _id: '3',
            name: "Fibonacci Search",
            algo: "def fibonacciSearch(array, searchingNumber):\n" +
                "    found = False\n" +
                "    f1 = 0\n" +
                "    f2 = 1\n" +
                "    f3 = 1\n" +
                "\n" +
                "    while f3 < (len(array) - 1):\n" +
                "        f1 = f2\n" +
                "        f2 = f3\n" +
                "        f3 = f1 + f2\n" +
                "\n" +
                "    low = 0\n" +
                "    index = -1\n" +
                "    high = len(array) - 1\n" +
                "\n" +
                "    while high >= low and not found:\n" +
                "        i = low + f2 - 1\n" +
                "        f3 = f2\n" +
                "        f2 = f1\n" +
                "        f1 = f3 - f2\n" +
                "\n" +
                "        if searchingNumber == array[i]:\n" +
                "            found = True\n" +
                "            index = i\n" +
                "\n" +
                "        else:\n" +
                "            if searchingNumber < array[i]:\n" +
                "                high = i - 1\n" +
                "\n" +
                "            else:\n" +
                "                low = i + 1\n" +
                "                f3 = f2\n" +
                "                f2 = f1\n" +
                "                f1 = f3 - f2\n" +
                "\n" +
                "    if found:\n" +
                "        print(\"Found at: \" + str(index))\n" +
                "\n" +
                "    else:\n" +
                "        print(\"Not found!\")"
        },
        {
            _id: '4',
            name: "Block Search",
            algo: "def blockSearch(array, searchingNumber):\n" +
                "    found = False\n" +
                "    size = math.sqrt(len(array))\n" +
                "    i = size\n" +
                "    j = len(array) - 1\n" +
                "\n" +
                "    if searchingNumber > array[j]:\n" +
                "        index = len(array)\n" +
                "        print(\"Found1: \" + str(index))\n" +
                "\n" +
                "    else:\n" +
                "        while i < len(interpolationSearch()):\n" +
                "            if searchingNumber <= array[i]:\n" +
                "                j = i\n" +
                "                i = len(array)\n" +
                "\n" +
                "            else:\n" +
                "                i = i + size\n" +
                "                if i > len(array) - 1:\n" +
                "                    i = len(array) - 1\n" +
                "\n" +
                "            i = j - size\n" +
                "            for i in j:\n" +
                "                if searchingNumber == array[i]:\n" +
                "                    index = i\n" +
                "                    found = True\n" +
                "                    break\n" +
                "                else:\n" +
                "                    if searchingNumber < array[i]:\n" +
                "                        index = i\n" +
                "                        break\n" +
                "\n" +
                "            if found:\n" +
                "                print(\"Found : \" + index)\n" +
                "            else:\n" +
                "                print(\"Not found\")"
        },
        {
            _id: '5',
            name: "Interpolation Search",
            algo: "def interpolationSearch(array, searchingNumber):\n" +
                "    found = False\n" +
                "    low = 0\n" +
                "    high = len(array) - 1\n" +
                "    while array[low] <= searchingNumber and searchingNumber <= array[high] and not found:\n" +
                "        f = float((high - low) / (array[high] - array[low]) * (searchingNumber - array[low]))\n" +
                "        mid = int(f + 0.5)\n" +
                "        i = mid + low\n" +
                "        if (searchingNumber == array[i]):\n" +
                "            found = True\n" +
                "            index = i\n" +
                "\n" +
                "        else:\n" +
                "            if searchingNumber > array[i]:\n" +
                "                low = i + 1\n" +
                "\n" +
                "            else:\n" +
                "                high = i - 1\n" +
                "\n" +
                "    if found == True:\n" +
                "        print(\"Found at: \" + str(index))\n" +
                "\n" +
                "    else:\n" +
                "        print(\"Not found!\")"
        }]
}
